# Carro — Tienda online Chile

Monolito **Laravel 13** + **PHP 8.4**. Frontend **Blade + Bootstrap 5** (sin Vue/React). API REST + Swagger. Pagos **Webpay Plus** (Transbank). BD **PostgreSQL** (carrito, órdenes, sesiones/cache en prod sin Redis).

Raíz del repo: `C:\Users\csoto\Documents\workspace84\carro`

## Stack y restricciones

- **No** usar Vue, React ni SPA separado para la tienda.
- **No** crear carpeta `backend/` — todo vive en la raíz Laravel (a diferencia de `ventaonline`).
- Controladores en `app/Http/` (nunca en `app/Models/Http/`).
- Locale: español (`es` / `es_CL`), timezone **`America/Santiago`** (`APP_TIMEZONE`).

## Estructura clave

```
app/Http/Controllers/Web/     → tienda Blade (Shop, Cart, Checkout, PaymentWeb)
app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/  → API REST + atributos OpenAPI
app/Http/Traits/ApiResponse.php → respuestas JSON { data, meta, errors }
app/Http/Middleware/EnsureAdmin.php → alias 'admin'
app/Services/CartService.php  → carro guest (cookie cart_session) + usuario
app/Services/OrderService.php
app/Services/ShippingService.php
app/Services/Payments/WebpayGateway.php
resources/views/shop/         → vistas tienda
resources/views/layouts/shop.blade.php → layout + loader overlay
public/css/shop.css, public/js/shop-loader.js, public/images/loading.*
routes/web.php, routes/api.php
config/l5-swagger.php, config/transbank.php, config/products.php
docker-compose.yml, docker/, Dockerfile, KOYEB.md
```

